<script>
// Address Search
$(function (){

	var submitted = false; // prevent multiple submits
	$('#frmSearch').submit(function(e){
		e.preventDefault();

		if (!submitted) {
			submitted = true;

			var searchAddress = $('#address').val().trim();

			try {
				var geocoder = new google.maps.Geocoder();
				geocoder.geocode({
					'address' : searchAddress
				}, function(results, status) {
					if (status == google.maps.GeocoderStatus.OK && results.length) {
						var point = results[0].geometry;
						lat = point.location.lat();
						lng = point.location.lng();

						var newUrl = "https://www.broadbandmap.gov/internet-service-providers/"+ searchAddress +"/lat="+ lat +"/long="+ lng +"/";
						location.href = newUrl;
						return false;
					}
					else {
						var newUrl = "https://www.broadbandmap.gov/internet-service-providers/" + searchAddress;
						location.href = newUrl;
						return false;
					}
				});

			} catch (e) {
				var newUrl = "https://www.broadbandmap.gov/internet-service-providers/" + searchAddress;
				location.href = newUrl;
				return false;
			}
		}
		else {
			return false;
		}
	});
});

/* end page load fade-in functionality */
$(window).load(function(){
	$('head:eq(0)').children('#stw').remove(); // Remove STYLE that was hiding the ShareThis IFRAME.
	$('#stLframe').attr('height','250px'); // Reduce the height of the IFRAME to prevent unnecessary scrollbar.
	/* Modified version of http://www.stefanoverna.com/log/create-astonishing-ical-like-calendars-with-jquery */
	$('.has-popup').delay(2000).each(function() {
		// options
		var distance = 9;
		var time = 200;
		var hideDelay = 300;
		var showDelay = 300;
		var hideDelayTimer = null;
		var showDelayTimer = null;
		// tracker
		var beingShown = false;
		var shown = false;
		var trigger = $(this).children('a');
		var popup = $('.popup-wrap', this).css('opacity', 0);
		// set the mouseover [and focus] and mouseout on both elements:
		$([trigger.get(0), popup.get(0)]).bind('mouseover focus', function () {
			// stops the hide event if we move from the trigger to the popup element
			if (hideDelayTimer) clearTimeout(hideDelayTimer);
			if (showDelayTimer) clearTimeout(showDelayTimer);

			// don't trigger the animation again if it's being shown, or already visible:
			if (beingShown || shown) {
				popup.css({zIndex: 999});
				return;
			} else {
				$('.popup-wrap').not(popup).css({zIndex: 998}).triggerHandler('mouseout'); // hide other popups
				showDelayTimer = setTimeout(function() {
					showDelayTimer = null;
					beingShown = true;
					// reset position of popup box
					popup.css({
						bottom: '7px',
						left: (0 - ((popup.outerWidth(true) / 2) + (trigger.width() / 2)) - 6),
						display: 'block', // brings the popup back in to view
						zIndex: 999
					})
					.stop().animate({
						bottom: '+=' + distance + 'px',
						opacity: 1
					}, time, 'swing', function() {
						beingShown = false;
						shown = true;
					});
				}, showDelay);
			}
		}).focus(function(){
			$('.has-popup > a').not($(this)).each(function(){
				$(this).triggerHandler('mouseout');
			});
		}).mouseout(function() {
			// reset the timer if we get fired again - avoids double animations
			if (hideDelayTimer) clearTimeout(hideDelayTimer);
			if (showDelayTimer) clearTimeout(showDelayTimer);
			// store the timer so that it can be cleared in the mouseover if required
			hideDelayTimer = setTimeout(function () {
				hideDelayTimer = null;
				popup.stop().animate({
					bottom: '-=' + distance + 'px',
					opacity: 0
				}, time, 'swing', function () {
					shown = false;
					popup.css('display', 'none'); // hide the popup entirely after the effect (opacity alone doesn't do the job)
				});
			}, hideDelay);
		}).blur(function(){
			popup.css({zIndex: 998});
		}).find('a').focus(function(){
			$(this).parents('.popup-wrap').css({zIndex: 999});
		});
	});
	//$('.btnProvider, .site-links a:eq(0)').focus(function(){
	$('#frmSearch > p a:last, .site-links a:eq(0)').focus(function(){
		$('.has-popup > a').each(function(){
			$(this).triggerHandler('mouseout');
		});
	});
	$.ajax({ // pre-fetch the OpenLayers script
		url: '/js/geo/openlayers/OpenLayers.js',
		cache: true,
		dataType: 'text'
	});
});
</script>
<script>
$('#dialog-bye').dialog({
	autoOpen: false,
	beforeClose: function(event, ui) { clearTimeout($.nbm_redirect); },
	close: function(event, ui) { if ($.nbm_dialogOrigin != null) $.nbm_dialogOrigin.focus(); },
	dialogClass: 'ui-dialog-bye',
	draggable: false,
	height: 240,
	hide: 'explode',
	modal: true,
	open: function(event, ui){
		$('#bye-note').focus();
		$('.ui-widget-overlay').click(function(){ $('#dialog-bye').dialog('dialogbeforeclose').dialog('close') });
		$.nbm_timedRedirect();
	},
	resizable: false,
	title: $('#dialog-bye h2:eq(1)').text(),
	width: 500,
	zIndex: 9000
}).find('h2:eq(1)').remove();
$.nbm_dialogOrigin = null;
$.nbm_redirect = null;
$.nbm_timedRedirect = function() { $.nbm_redirect = setTimeout("window.location = $('#dialog-bye .destination').attr('href')", 5000); }

$.nbm_goodbye = function(anchor){
	$.nbm_dialogOrigin = $(anchor);
	var url = unescape($(anchor).attr('href'));
	url = url.substring(url.lastIndexOf('http'), url.length);
	$('#dialog-bye strong').html('<a class="destination" href="' + url + '">' + $(anchor).text() + ' [ ' + url + ' ]</a>');
	$('#dialog-bye').dialog('open');
	return false;
}

$('a[href*="/external-redirect/http://"]').not('[onclick*="$.nbm_goodbye("]').each(function(i, item){
	$(item).click(function(e){
		$.nbm_goodbye(item);
		return false;
	});
});

$('#dialog-warning').find('h2:eq(0)').hide().end().dialog({
	dialogClass: 'ui-dialog-warning',
	close: function(event, ui) { $('a:first').focus(); },
	height: 240,
	hide: 'explode',
	modal: true,
	open: function(event, ui){ window.setTimeout("$('html, body').animate({scrollTop: 0});", 600); },
	resizable: false,
	title: $('#dialog-warning h2:eq(0)').text(),
	width: 500,
	zIndex: 9000
});

$('html').delegate('.ui-widget-overlay', 'click', function(){
	$($('.ui-dialog-bye').is(':visible') ? '#dialog-bye' : '#dialog-warning').dialog('dialogbeforeclose').dialog('close');
});
</script></body>
</html>
